What you need to know:  Kip Keino Classic meet director Barnaba Korir disclosed Saturday that the 32-year-old Fajdek, who won bronze at the Olympics, is in a rich list of hammer throwers due for the World Athletics Continental Gold Tour eventFajdek, who weighs 128kgs beat Olympic champion Wojciech Nowicki, hauling a new Meet Record of 78.33m to win in Nairobi last yearKorir noted that what will make the third edition unique following the success of the October 2020 and September 2021 editions is the presence of fans